
<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container ml-16 py-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-white flex flex-col w-full">
  <!-- Title Section -->
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-violet-500">How to Use Questrack</h1>

  <!-- Step 1 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 1: Sign Up or Log In</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      To start using Questrack, you'll first need to create an account or log in if you already have one.
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2">
        <li>Click on the <strong>"Sign Up"</strong> button at the top right of the homepage.</li>
        <li>Fill in your basic details such as name, email, and password.</li>
        <li>If you already have an account, simply click <strong>"Log In"</strong> and enter your credentials.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 2 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 2: Create a New Challenge</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      After logging in, you'll be directed to your dashboard where you can create your first challenge.
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2">
        <li>Click on the <strong>"Create Challenge"</strong> button.</li>
        <li>Fill in the challenge name, duration (e.g., 30 days, 60 days and 100 days), and description.</li>
        <li>Click <strong>"Submit"</strong> to save your new challenge.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 3 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 3: View Your Challenges</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Once your challenge is created, it will appear in your <strong>Challenges List</strong>.
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2">
        <li>Click on a challenge to view the details, such as the start date, end date, and your progress.</li>
        <li>You can track your daily progress and add notes for each day.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 4 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 4: Add Daily Notes</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      For each day in your challenge, Questrack allows you to write a journal entry:
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2">
        <li>Navigate to the challenge by clicking on it from your Challenges List.</li>
        <li>You'll see the day being clickable for each new day.</li>
        <li>In the note creation page, you can:
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2">
            <li>Enter a <strong>title for your day</strong>, summarizing the main highlight.</li>
            <li>Write your daily note or thoughts in the <strong>text box</strong> provided.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Once done, click <strong>"Create Note"</strong> to save your entry.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 5 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 5: View and Edit Notes</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      All your notes for a challenge are accessible from the challenge's detail page.
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2">
        <li>Click on any day to view or edit your note for that specific day.</li>
        <li>To edit, click the <strong>"Edit"</strong> button, modify your note or title, and click <strong>"Save Changes"</strong>.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Step 6 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 6: Track Your Progress</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Questrack allows you to see your overall progress in a visually intuitive way.
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2">
        <li>On the challenge detail page, you'll see a progress bar indicating how many days you’ve completed.</li>
        <li>This motivates you to stay on track and complete the challenge.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 8 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 7: Explore Other Features</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      You can also <strong>navigate</strong> through the app’s different sections such as <strong>Explore</strong>, where you might discover community-based challenges, and <strong>My Profile</strong>, where you can update your details or track your overall app usage.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 9 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 8: Stay Motivated</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Questrack is designed to keep you motivated throughout your challenge. Use the journaling feature to reflect on your progress and celebrate your wins!
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 10 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Step 9: Feedback and Support</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      If you encounter any issues or have feedback, simply navigate to the <strong><a class="underline decoration-cyan-500 decoration-2 hover:decoration-4 duration-300" href="https://github.com/codistiano/questrack">Github Issues</a></strong> of the app, and I'll be happy to assist you!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

